#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Bags" field of the "Distributor" table</h2>
This field is a comma separated list of things that almost every patron receives every time,
the "shipping unit".  For instance:
    <div class=field_format>Freezer,Refrigerator</div>
This information is used to determine what bags should be picked up from the distribution
center's distribution center.

